  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 5th level, once per turn when you deal 15 or more Poison damage to a creature in a single instance, you can impose a Constitution saving throw against your Ninjutsu or Taijutsu Save DC.</p><p> On a failed save, the creature becomes Envenomed for 1 minute.</p><p> At 13th level, you ignore Resistance to the Envenomed condition, as well as Poison damage, with your Sour Snacks, and treat Immunity as Resistance.</p><p> Additionally, when you deal Poison damage to a creature with 2 or more ranks of Envenomed and they would fail the Constitution saving throw imposed by this feature, you can choose to make them Dazed alongside being Envenomed, or increase the Envenomed condition's damage by 1 step for the duration.</p><p></p>",
